324
00:47:25,863 --> 00:47:28,543
Nije uvek bilo tako.

325
00:47:33,000 --> 00:47:38,473
Salazar je vodio liniju s ponosom.

326
00:47:38,474 --> 00:47:42,798
Ovde se znao red.

327
00:47:42,799 --> 00:47:45,605
Postovalo se.

328
00:47:45,606 --> 00:47:48,484
