371
00:54:09,481 --> 00:54:11,074
Postovali?

372
00:54:11,075 --> 00:54:15,105
Dozvolili smo da prodje ona
stvar u Nikaragvi i...

373
00:54:15,106 --> 00:54:18,886
napravio si gomilu para na racun
one svinje, Eskobara i...

374
00:54:18,887 --> 00:54:25,091
