mi smo se pobrinuli za to.

375
00:54:25,092 --> 00:54:27,204
Jel se secas?

376
00:54:27,205 --> 00:54:31,529
Iskreno, nas zabole za to sto
vi ovde radite.

377
00:54:33,468 --> 00:54:35,698
