405
00:59:41,698 --> 00:59:43,990
Nemam pojma.

406
00:59:43,991 --> 00:59:46,215
Nikad ga ustvari nisam poznavala.

407
00:59:46,216 --> 00:59:49,374
Bila sam na metadonu.

408
00:59:49,375 --> 00:59:52,916
Bilo je puno muskaraca.

409
00:59:59,909 --> 01:00:01,708
Vec 5 meseci.

